- Use function components + hooks; avoid class components.
- React Query for server state; no Redux unless necessary.
- Co-locate components/hooks/tests; keep components small.
- Memoize with React.memo/useMemo/useCallback based on profiling.
- Prefer controlled inputs; avoid unnecessary local state.
- Error boundaries around complex/render-heavy sections.
- Code-split heavy routes/components; lazy-load charts/analytics.

